cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this code or notebook in your work, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "MIN-K% Prob: Detecting Pretraining Data from LLMs — Reproduction & Analysis"
abstract: >
  A reproduction and analysis of the MIN-K% Prob membership inference method
  from the ICLR 2024 paper "Detecting Pretraining Data from Large Language Models"
  by Shi et al. Includes a toy memorisation experiment, head-to-head MIA comparison,
  WikiMIA benchmark evaluation, hyperparameter sweep, and multi-model scaling study.
